<div class="title">Wowie Wow Wow!</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B & MDMA</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bluedolphin&Exact=1">Bluedolphin</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bluedolphin. "Wowie Wow Wow!: An Experience with 2C-B & MDMA (exp46853)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 4, 2008. erowid.org/exp/46853</div>

